{"tid":604131,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人同老豆冇傾計","createTime":"2018-03-24T12:06:14.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-24T12:33:57.000Z","uid":143190,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"ca7624f52945765974602e632361c09846a71272","tid":604131,"uid":143190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-24T12:06:14.000Z","msg":"我成年同老豆講野都唔過十句<br />\n有一次佢冇啦啦入我間房 話兩仔爺講心下事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個下我立即覺得好肉麻 冇理到佢<br />\n相反同老母就好多野講 關係好好 <br />\n其實同老豆關係都唔差 但係唔識開口搵話題 一開心講野個情況就好尷尬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1c37bdd87edd335138982fec92dfabd9ba673af","tid":604131,"uid":20291,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-24T12:19:58.000Z","msg":"由細到大都未叫過老豆呢2個字，呀媽到呢幾年都少叫"},{"pid":"262aaa5bdda4ee5b9d5ee52f2e587dce99937f5b","tid":604131,"uid":102096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-24T12:23:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a586f4925bc89b6f1f32a03dd1ea5732cd63fe27","tid":604131,"uid":140022,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-24T12:24:48.000Z","msg":"同樓主一樣<br />\n關係都唔差 但係唔識開口搵話題 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c52630ef798589f38834de70443c6d4e84d85a0a","tid":604131,"uid":71712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-24T12:33:57.000Z","msg":"關係差 講多句就互屌 廢撚事講"}]}